		<li class="question">Q: What is the elo rating system and how does it work?</li><br>
		<li class="answer">A: The Elo Rating system was originally created by Arpad Elo for chess players that seeks to compute the relative skills of competitors when two players competed against one another. In the case of this website, the Elo Rating system is used to objectively rank the quality of art using head-to-head competition. Existing websites tend to promote art by popularity but the Elo system avoids this problem. The Elo system rapidly promotes high performing submissions and provides a system of checks and balances which does not have an intense bias toward popularity and longevity.
		</li><hr class="line">

