		<li class="question">Q: How do I find interesting art to vote on? </li><br>
		<li class="answer">A: Simply click vote on the upper left and choose which tag you want to vote under!</li><hr class="line">

		<li class="question">Q: Why don’t I have access to all the artist’s images/videos when I visit their profile page?</li><br>
		<li class="answer">A: You will not be able to see art that you have not voted on yet. This is to prevent bias toward that particular artist. We want votes to be judged solely on the quality of the art and not be lured by who made it.</li><hr class="line">

